description: Coefficients of monic primitive irreducible polynomials over GF(4) listed in lexicographic order.
comments: The elements of GF(4) are labeled {0,1,2,3}.
references: D. H. Green and I. S. Taylor, Irreducible polynomials over composite Galois fields and their applications in coding techniques, Proc. IEE, 121 (1974), 935-939.
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_, Jan 13 2001
extensions: Green and Taylor's table extends through degree 5.
